d-5787-402a-b339-cd5967c717de\"><strong>เวลาในการชำระบัญชี</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"365\"><p data-block-id=\"a87d280c-5335-4fc9-9209-3f1b25c8fa90\">ทันที</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"235\" style=\"background-color:#ffffff;\"><p data-block-id=\"0b1acf11-6c69-4fa4-8cef-2c20e9a57f9f\"><strong>การคืนเงิน</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"365\"><p data-block-id=\"51e5fb56-c4f1-4bcd-ae0b-bac64fa6efa9\">&#x274c;</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"235\" style=\"background-color:#ffffff;\"><p data-block-id=\"c5b1b451-9474-4afc-a147-7abb2b3914b5\"><strong>การคืนเงินบางส่วน</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"365\"><p data-block-id=\"9f561b43-4a14-4021-875d-2cf4ed4b6ada\">&#x274c;</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"235\" style=\"background-color:#ffffff;\"><p data-block-id=\"ab7efb01-7e12-4c3e-8e97-3e21f1b69fcf\"><strong>การคืนเงินบางส่วนหลายครั้ง</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"365\"><p data-block-id=\"7bfba827-4346-466b-967f-96e5c3815401\">&#x274c;</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"235\" style=\"background-color:#ffffff;\"><p data-block-id=\"79e9de91-89e5-461a-a976-bdccee4a4dd7\"><strong>ความถูกต้องของการคืนเงิน</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"365\"><p data-block-id=\"980f78d2-e091-426e-a79f-83c85cb968ee\">&#x274c;</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"235\" style=\"background-color:#ffffff;\"><p data-block-id=\"me1437v5-ukd5lz-157\"><strong>ข้อมูลผู้ใช้ที่ธนาคารต้องการ*</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"365\"><ul data-block-id=\"me1446oq-saxr81-159\"><li data-block-id=\"me1446oq-ol9k66-160\"><p data-block-id=\"me1445gs-z8rj4c-158\">หมายเลขโทรศัพท์มือถือ</p></li><li data-block-id=\"me1446oq-ol9k66-160\"><p data-block-id=\"me1445gs-z8rj4c-158\">หมายเลขบัตรประจำตัวประชาชนหรือหมายเลขหนังสือเดินทาง</p></li></ul></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"235\" style=\"background-color:#ffffff;\"><p data-block-id=\"9f8270e5-fafe-4128-abe3-b85f9c67e07d\"><strong>การผสานรวมที่เข้ากันได้</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"365\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"01aa413c-90f2-4b3e-8a19-924838f3f649\">Payment API, Payment Session, Subscription, Recurring</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p data-block-id=\"me1428fo-0cai1g-155\">*ธนาคารจะตรวจสอบความถูกต้องของข้อมูลการเข้าสู่ระบบกับหมายเลขโทรศัพท์มือถือและหมายเลขบัตรประจำตัวประชาชนที่ส่งมาระหว่างการร้องขอ Payment Request</p><h2 data-block-id=\"cfdaf3d6-9051-4523-8aaa-f70aa85edcd9\">ขั้นตอนการเชื่อมโยงบัญชี</h2><p data-block-id=\"me13qr2c-3sfj2q-133\">ลูกค้าปลายทางเลือกธนาคารเพื่อเชื่อมโยงในหน้าชำระเงินและดำเนินการอนุมัติ (Account Linking)</p><p data-block-id=\"me13q013-de0ivg-132\"><img data-block-id=\"me13tlwy-23uwbq-150\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/Payment session - DD linking.jpg\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"277\" height=\"337\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link newtab style=\"width:277px;height:337px;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"me0xf87f-gez1lt-073\"><img data-block-id=\"me14mm7d-hwpiz8-222\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/KTB DD.jpg\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"ขั้นตอนการเชื่อมโยงบัญชีธนาคารโดยใช้แอป Krungthai NEXT สำหรับการทำธุรกรรม\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link newtab></p><p data-block-id=\"me13krcu-exjbt7-118\"></p>","SeoTitle":"KTB Direct Debit","Description":null},{"Code":"es-mx","Title":"KTB Direct Debit","Slug":"ktb-direct-debit","ContentType":2,"Content":"<style> p[data-block-id] {font-size:1rem;} ul li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ul[data-type=\"taskList\"] li div p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ol li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} table tbody th p[data-block-id] { margin-bottom: 0;} blockquote p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0 !important;}  p[data-block-id]:empty::after {content: \"\\00A0\";} </style><p data-block-id=\"d987c8f4-49c5-47f5-9088-b3c739b1e097\"></p><hr class=\"hr-divider1\"><h2 data-block-id=\"e8847995-c7ee-4260-aa73-f29d7ec2ab89\">Características &amp; Requisitos</h2><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"600\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\" style=\"max-width:600px;width:600px;\"><colgroup><col style=\"width:235px;\"><col style=\"width:365px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"235\" style=\"background-color:#ffffff;\"><p data-block-id=\"a7b3243a-a519-4533-9196-d56c3a295943\"><strong>Código del Canal</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"365\"><p data-block-id=\"04011f79-3d6a-403b-ad9d-142c2f2c6633\"><code>KTB_DIRECT_DEBIT</code></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"235\" style=\"background-color:#ffffff;\"><p data-block-id=\"d3146c4b-f4ee-4d2c-99c6-95d1d8a3992f\"><strong>Moneda</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"365\"><p data-block-id=\"8f8f52c4-849b-4eb7-ab70-b2612e4b910b\">THB</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"235\" style=\"background-color:#ffffff;\"><p data-block-id=\"5d5914ce-966d-482b-8884-2052379bf789\"><strong>Monto Mínimo</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"365\"><p data-block-id=\"c5f6c861-98e4-4b48-9a14-8823d1683a2f\">20</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"235\" style=\"background-color:#ffffff;\"><p data-block-id=\"314c0e0d-1fa4-4dc4-9b90-0bcd960b7f9d\"><strong>Monto Máximo</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"365\"><p data-block-id=\"e27cf842-8ec0-4091-a59c-ed438a464063\">700,000</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"235\" style=\"background-color:#ffffff;\"><p data-block-id=\"172d356b-db4c-427d-9b05-faf0c987829c\"><strong>Flujo de aprobación del Cliente</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"365\"><p data-block-id=\"5df88d59-b234-4363-b5f8-119e8204136a\">REDIRECT</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"235\" style=\"background-color:#ffffff;\"><p data-block-id=\"cf4c8e16-56ad-4379-8d03-3934188e6395\"><strong>Guardar</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"365\"><p data-block-id=\"6a980828-0315-4889-9c68-28432de9a672\">&#x2705;</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"235\" style=\"background-color:#ffffff;\"><p data-block-id=\"e9710e04-aeed-4dc0-a181-221896b27c47\"><strong>Recurrente</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"365\"><p data-block-id=\"01e3a16a-13f6-4fcf-9f5f-9f81493dd29c\">&#x2705;</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"235\" style=\"background-color:#ffffff;\"><p data-block-id=\"b91bea40-48ad-49f9-a6da-773586bb341d\"><strong>Mostrar nombre del Comercio</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"365\"><p data-block-id=\"4c4b1311-2263-40d7-a444-da070eb2d45e\">Xendit</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"235\" style=\"background-color:#ffffff;\"><p data-block-id=\"30c42a0d-04a0-49d8-bed5-b6f97cb2d4c6\"><strong>Mostrar nombre del Cliente</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"365\"><p data-block-id=\"e887748f-2f71-44ed-8a13-07c6f6775bb4\">&#x274c;</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"235\" style=\"background-color:#ffffff;\"><p data-block-id=\"dc107acc-5ecf-4b96-bb5a-8dc60e638d0d\"><strong>Establecer expiración</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"365\"><p data-block-id=\"b87a15b2-ca3a-4c76-a09e-2fd8b2a174f0\">&#x274c;</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"235\" style=\"background-color:#ffffff;\"><p data-block-id=\"7a5cbe3d-5787-402a-b339-cd5967c717de\"><strong>Tiempo de Liquidación</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"365\"><p data-block-id=\"a87d280c-5335-4fc9-9209-3f1b25c8fa90\">Instant</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"235\" style=\"background-color:#ffffff;\"><p data-block-id=\"0b1acf11-6c69-4fa4-8cef-2c20e9a57f9f\"><strong>Reembolso</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"365\"><p data-block-id=\"51e5fb56-c4f1-4bcd-ae0b-bac64fa6efa9\">&#x274c;</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"235\" style=\"background-color:#ffffff;\"><p data-block-id=\"c5b1b451-9474-4afc-a147-7abb2b3914b5\"><strong>Reembolso Parcial</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"365\"><p data-block-id=\"9f561b43-4a14-4021-875d-2cf4ed4b6ada\">&#x274c;</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"235\" style=\"background-color:#ffffff;\"><p data-block-id=\"ab7efb01-7e12-4c3e-8e97-3e21f1b69fcf\"><strong>Múltiples reembolsos parciales</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"365\"><p data-block-id=\"7bfba827-4346-466b-967f-96e5c3815401\">&#x274c;</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"235\" style=\"background-color:#ffffff;\"><p data-block-id=\"79e9de91-89e5-461a-a976-bdccee4a4dd7\"><strong>Validez del Reembolso</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"365\"><p data-block-id=\"980f78d2-e091-426e-a79f-83c85cb968ee\">&#x274c;</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"235\" style=\"background-color:#ffffff;\"><p data-block-id=\"me1437v5-ukd5lz-157\"><strong>Datos del Cliente requeridos por el Banco*</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"365\"><ul data-block-id=\"me1446oq-saxr81-159\"><li data-block-id=\"me1446oq-ol9k66-160\"><p data-block-id=\"me1445gs-z8rj4c-158\">Número de Teléfono Móvil</p></li><li data-block-id=\"me1446oq-ol9k66-160\"><p data-block-id=\"me1445gs-z8rj4c-158\">Número de Identidad o Número de Pasaporte</p></li></ul></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"235\" style=\"background-color:#ffffff;\"><p data-block-id=\"9f8270e5-fafe-4128-abe3-b85f9c67e07d\"><strong>Integración Compatible</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"365\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"01aa413c-90f2-4b3e-8a19-924838f3f649\">Payment API, Payment Session, Subscription, Recurring</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p data-block-id=\"me1428fo-0cai1g-155\">*El Banco validará la credencial de inicio de sesión con el número de teléfono móvil y el número de ID enviados durante la Solicitud de Pago (Payment Request)</p><h2 data-block-id=\"cfdaf3d6-9051-4523-8aaa-f70aa85edcd9\">Flujo de Vinculación de Cuenta</h2><p data-block-id=\"me13qr2c-3sfj2q-133\">El cliente final selecciona el banco a vincular en la página de pago y procesa la autorización (Account Linking)</p><p data-block-id=\"me13q013-de0ivg-132\"><img data-block-id=\"me13tlwy-23uwbq-150\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/Payment session - DD linking.jpg\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"277\" height=\"337\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link newtab style=\"width:277px;height:337px;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"me0xf87f-gez1lt-073\"><img data-block-id=\"me14mm7d-hwpiz8-222\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/KTB DD.jpg\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"Pasos para vincular una cuenta bancaria usando la aplicación Krungthai NEXT para transacciones.\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link newtab></p><p data-block-id=\"me13krcu-exjbt7-118\"></p>","SeoTitle":"KTB Direct Debit","Description":null}]